        "TileImage": "$($repository a6b36d85-50ba-44a7-9bd8-47e17c7cf560).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47.  \r\rHaven Island needs to cut costs and is currently laying off staff. The lifeguards are next on the chopping board, but work contracts make the departure expensive with the lifeguards being unwilling to  budge.\r\rThe client wants to get rid of the problematic lifeguards, in an apparently ironic way, if possible.",
